      <TextArea layoutX="40.0" layoutY="434.0" prefHeight="56.0" prefWidth="254.0" text="*Stay alert and attentive during duty&#10;*Communicate clearly with team members&#10;*Maintain professionalism at all times&#10;*Assist guests and VIPs respectfully* Be aware of match schedule and assigned duty zones&#10;* Monitor VIP areas and player zones carefully&#10;* Ensure crowd control at entry and exit points&#10;* Coordinate with event managers and staff" />
